===Week 10: vs. Jacksonville Jaguars===
{{Americanfootballbox|
|Road='''Jaguars'''
|R1=7||R2=14||R3=0||R4=3
|Home=Jets
|H1=10||H2=3||H3=0||H4=9
|stadium= [[Giants Stadium]], [[East Rutherford, New Jersey]]
|time= 1:00&nbsp;pm [[North American Eastern Time Zone|EST]]
|weather= 62 Â°F (Cloudy)<ref name="week 10 gb">{{cite web|url=http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/54600/NYJ_Gamebook.pdf|title=Jacksonville Jaguars at New York Jets Gamebook|publisher=National Football League|date=November 15, 2009|accessdate=January 27, 2010}}</ref>
|attendance= 76,313<ref name="week 10 gb"/>
|referee= [[Ed Hochuli]]<ref name="week 10 gb"/>
|TV=[[NFL on CBS|CBS]] |TVAnnouncers= [[Dick Enberg]] & [[Dan Fouts]]
