===Week 16: at Indianapolis Colts===
{{Americanfootballbox|
|Road='''Jets'''
|R1=0||R2=3||R3=15||R4=11||RT=
|Home=Colts
|H1=6||H2=3||H3=6||H4=0||HT=
|stadium= [[Lucas Oil Stadium]], [[Indianapolis, Indiana]]
|time= 4:15&nbsp;pm [[North American Eastern Time Zone|EST]]
|weather= None (Roof Closed)<ref name="week 16 gb">{{cite web|url=http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/54704/IND_Gamebook.pdf|title=New York Jets at Indianapolis Colts Gamebook|publisher=National Football League|date=December 27, 2009|accessdate=January 27, 2010}}</ref>
|attendance= 67,222<ref name="week 16 gb"/>
|referee= [[Terry McAulay]]<ref name="week 16 gb"/>
|TV=[[NFL on CBS|CBS]] |TVAnnouncers= [[Greg Gumbel]] and [[Dan Dierdorf]]
