With the win, the Jets ended the Colts' perfect season run, and also ended their 23âgame regular season winning streak.  The Jets were able to capitalize on the Colts' decision to bench quarterback Peyton Manning to avoid injury given they had already made the playoffs.  The Jets improved their playoff chances greatly by moving to 8â7 on the season.

